{"title":"ZhengRui2022暑期集训培训日记Day12","uid":"c0cc46f365444ef3eca9da6a194500f6","text":"T1 不难想到根号分治，考虑小小合并复杂度显然正确，大大合并，如果所有大的都是 级别，那么复杂度正确，如果一个变多，那么对数也会接着减少，不难分析复杂度其实是没有减少的，所以复杂度正切，考虑大小怎么做，一个套路的想法是对于小大询问的每一个大，把对应的所有的小拿出来，注意到小的权值...","date":"2022-08-13T12:25:41.000Z","updated":"2022-08-13T12:31:30.799Z","comments":true,"path":"api/pages/hiden/ZhengRui2022暑期集训培训日记Day12.json","covers":null,"excerpt":"","content":"<h1 id=\"t1\">T1</h1>\n<p>不难想到根号分治，考虑小小合并复杂度显然正确，大大合并，如果所有大的都是 <span class=\"math inline\"><mjx-container class=\"MathJax\" jax=\"SVG\"><svg style=\"vertical-align: -0.491ex\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"3.287ex\" height=\"2.398ex\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" viewBox=\"0 -843 1453 1060\"><g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"scale(1,-1)\"><g data-mml-node=\"math\"><g data-mml-node=\"msqrt\"><g transform=\"translate(853,0)\"><g data-mml-node=\"mi\"><path data-c=\"1D45B\" d=\"M21 287Q22 293 24 303T36 341T56 388T89 425T135 442Q171 442 195 424T225 390T231 369Q231 367 232 367L243 378Q304 442 382 442Q436 442 469 415T503 336T465 179T427 52Q427 26 444 26Q450 26 453 27Q482 32 505 65T540 145Q542 153 560 153Q580 153 580 145Q580 144 576 130Q568 101 554 73T508 17T439 -10Q392 -10 371 17T350 73Q350 92 386 193T423 345Q423 404 379 404H374Q288 404 229 303L222 291L189 157Q156 26 151 16Q138 -11 108 -11Q95 -11 87 -5T76 7T74 17Q74 30 112 180T152 343Q153 348 153 366Q153 405 129 405Q91 405 66 305Q60 285 60 284Q58 278 41 278H27Q21 284 21 287Z\"></path></g></g><g data-mml-node=\"mo\" transform=\"translate(0,-17)\"><path data-c=\"221A\" d=\"M95 178Q89 178 81 186T72 200T103 230T169 280T207 309Q209 311 212 311H213Q219 311 227 294T281 177Q300 134 312 108L397 -77Q398 -77 501 136T707 565T814 786Q820 800 834 800Q841 800 846 794T853 782V776L620 293L385 -193Q381 -200 366 -200Q357 -200 354 -197Q352 -195 256 15L160 225L144 214Q129 202 113 190T95 178Z\"></path></g><rect width=\"600\" height=\"60\" x=\"853\" y=\"723\"></rect></g></g></g></svg></mjx-container></span> 级别，那么复杂度正确，如果一个变多，那么对数也会接着减少，不难分析复杂度其实是没有减少的，所以复杂度正切，考虑大小怎么做，一个套路的想法是对于小大询问的每一个大，把对应的所有的小拿出来，注意到小的权值重复的很多，对于一种长度，我们可以暴力枚举大的上面对应位置的和，接着只需要用小的长度的代价来回答询问。大的一共有 <span class=\"math inline\"><mjx-container class=\"MathJax\" jax=\"SVG\"><svg style=\"vertical-align: -0.491ex\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"3.287ex\" height=\"2.398ex\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" viewBox=\"0 -843 1453 1060\"><g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"scale(1,-1)\"><g data-mml-node=\"math\"><g data-mml-node=\"msqrt\"><g transform=\"translate(853,0)\"><g data-mml-node=\"mi\"><path data-c=\"1D45B\" d=\"M21 287Q22 293 24 303T36 341T56 388T89 425T135 442Q171 442 195 424T225 390T231 369Q231 367 232 367L243 378Q304 442 382 442Q436 442 469 415T503 336T465 179T427 52Q427 26 444 26Q450 26 453 27Q482 32 505 65T540 145Q542 153 560 153Q580 153 580 145Q580 144 576 130Q568 101 554 73T508 17T439 -10Q392 -10 371 17T350 73Q350 92 386 193T423 345Q423 404 379 404H374Q288 404 229 303L222 291L189 157Q156 26 151 16Q138 -11 108 -11Q95 -11 87 -5T76 7T74 17Q74 30 112 180T152 343Q153 348 153 366Q153 405 129 405Q91 405 66 305Q60 285 60 284Q58 278 41 278H27Q21 284 21 287Z\"></path></g></g><g data-mml-node=\"mo\" transform=\"translate(0,-17)\"><path data-c=\"221A\" d=\"M95 178Q89 178 81 186T72 200T103 230T169 280T207 309Q209 311 212 311H213Q219 311 227 294T281 177Q300 134 312 108L397 -77Q398 -77 501 136T707 565T814 786Q820 800 834 800Q841 800 846 794T853 782V776L620 293L385 -193Q381 -200 366 -200Q357 -200 354 -197Q352 -195 256 15L160 225L144 214Q129 202 113 190T95 178Z\"></path></g><rect width=\"600\" height=\"60\" x=\"853\" y=\"723\"></rect></g></g></g></svg></mjx-container></span> 个，每次处理也是 <span class=\"math inline\"><mjx-container class=\"MathJax\" jax=\"SVG\"><svg style=\"vertical-align: -0.491ex\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"3.287ex\" height=\"2.398ex\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" viewBox=\"0 -843 1453 1060\"><g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"scale(1,-1)\"><g data-mml-node=\"math\"><g data-mml-node=\"msqrt\"><g transform=\"translate(853,0)\"><g data-mml-node=\"mi\"><path data-c=\"1D45B\" d=\"M21 287Q22 293 24 303T36 341T56 388T89 425T135 442Q171 442 195 424T225 390T231 369Q231 367 232 367L243 378Q304 442 382 442Q436 442 469 415T503 336T465 179T427 52Q427 26 444 26Q450 26 453 27Q482 32 505 65T540 145Q542 153 560 153Q580 153 580 145Q580 144 576 130Q568 101 554 73T508 17T439 -10Q392 -10 371 17T350 73Q350 92 386 193T423 345Q423 404 379 404H374Q288 404 229 303L222 291L189 157Q156 26 151 16Q138 -11 108 -11Q95 -11 87 -5T76 7T74 17Q74 30 112 180T152 343Q153 348 153 366Q153 405 129 405Q91 405 66 305Q60 285 60 284Q58 278 41 278H27Q21 284 21 287Z\"></path></g></g><g data-mml-node=\"mo\" transform=\"translate(0,-17)\"><path data-c=\"221A\" d=\"M95 178Q89 178 81 186T72 200T103 230T169 280T207 309Q209 311 212 311H213Q219 311 227 294T281 177Q300 134 312 108L397 -77Q398 -77 501 136T707 565T814 786Q820 800 834 800Q841 800 846 794T853 782V776L620 293L385 -193Q381 -200 366 -200Q357 -200 354 -197Q352 -195 256 15L160 225L144 214Q129 202 113 190T95 178Z\"></path></g><rect width=\"600\" height=\"60\" x=\"853\" y=\"723\"></rect></g></g></g></svg></mjx-container></span> 的，前者会随着后者的增加而减少，可以分析其实是一样的。注意到剩下的部分对于每个大的是只有 <span class=\"math inline\"><mjx-container class=\"MathJax\" jax=\"SVG\"><svg style=\"vertical-align: -0.491ex\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"3.287ex\" height=\"2.398ex\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" viewBox=\"0 -843 1453 1060\"><g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"scale(1,-1)\"><g data-mml-node=\"math\"><g data-mml-node=\"msqrt\"><g transform=\"translate(853,0)\"><g data-mml-node=\"mi\"><path data-c=\"1D45B\" d=\"M21 287Q22 293 24 303T36 341T56 388T89 425T135 442Q171 442 195 424T225 390T231 369Q231 367 232 367L243 378Q304 442 382 442Q436 442 469 415T503 336T465 179T427 52Q427 26 444 26Q450 26 453 27Q482 32 505 65T540 145Q542 153 560 153Q580 153 580 145Q580 144 576 130Q568 101 554 73T508 17T439 -10Q392 -10 371 17T350 73Q350 92 386 193T423 345Q423 404 379 404H374Q288 404 229 303L222 291L189 157Q156 26 151 16Q138 -11 108 -11Q95 -11 87 -5T76 7T74 17Q74 30 112 180T152 343Q153 348 153 366Q153 405 129 405Q91 405 66 305Q60 285 60 284Q58 278 41 278H27Q21 284 21 287Z\"></path></g></g><g data-mml-node=\"mo\" transform=\"translate(0,-17)\"><path data-c=\"221A\" d=\"M95 178Q89 178 81 186T72 200T103 230T169 280T207 309Q209 311 212 311H213Q219 311 227 294T281 177Q300 134 312 108L397 -77Q398 -77 501 136T707 565T814 786Q820 800 834 800Q841 800 846 794T853 782V776L620 293L385 -193Q381 -200 366 -200Q357 -200 354 -197Q352 -195 256 15L160 225L144 214Q129 202 113 190T95 178Z\"></path></g><rect width=\"600\" height=\"60\" x=\"853\" y=\"723\"></rect></g></g></g></svg></mjx-container></span> 本质不同的长度，所以复杂度是正确的。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;\n#define mset(a,b) memset((a),(b),sizeof((a)))\n#define rep(i,l,r) for(int i=(l);i&lt;=(r);i++)\n#define dec(i,l,r) for(int i=(r);i&gt;=(l);i--)\n#define cmax(a,b) (((a)&lt;(b))?(a=b):(a))\n#define cmin(a,b) (((a)&gt;(b))?(a=b):(a))\n#define Next(k) for(int x=head[k];x;x=li[x].next)\n#define vc vector\n#define ar array\n#define pi pair\n#define fi first\n#define se second\n#define mp make_pair\n#define pb push_back\n#define N 200010\n#define M number\nusing namespace std;\n\ntypedef double dd;\ntypedef long double ld;\ntypedef long long ll;\ntypedef unsigned int uint;\ntypedef unsigned long long ull;\n#define int long long\ntypedef pair&lt;int,int&gt; P;\ntypedef vector&lt;int&gt; vi;\n\nconst int INF=0x3f3f3f3f;\nconst dd eps=1e-9;\nconst int mod=998244353;\n\ntemplate&lt;typename T&gt; inline void read(T &amp;x) {\n    x=0; int f=1;\n    char c=getchar();\n    for(;!isdigit(c);c=getchar()) if(c == '-') f=-f;\n    for(;isdigit(c);c=getchar()) x=x*10+c-'0';\n    x*=f;\n}\n\nint n,m,Len,ans[N],Tm[N];\nvi v[N];\nmap&lt;P,int&gt; Map;\nstruct Ques{\n    int x,id;\n    inline bool operator &lt; (const Ques &amp;b)const{return v[x].size()&lt;v[b.x].size();}\n};\nvc&lt;Ques&gt; q[N];\n\ninline int Solve(int a,int b){\n    int Ans=0;if(v[a].size()&gt;v[b].size()) swap(a,b);\n    int lena=v[a].size(),lenb=v[b].size();\n    rep(i,0,lenb-1){\n        Ans+=v[a][i%lena]*v[b][i]%mod;\n        Ans%=mod;\n    } \n    // printf(\"Ans=%lld\\n\",Ans);\n    return Ans;\n}\ninline int Solve2(int a,int b){\n    if(v[a].size()&gt;v[b].size())  swap(a,b);\n    if(Map.find({a,b})!=Map.end()) return Map[{a,b}];\n    int Ans=0,lena=v[a].size(),lenb=v[b].size(); \n    // printf(\"a=%d b=%d lena=%d lenb=%d\\n\",a,b,lena,lenb);\n    rep(i,0,lenb-1){\n        Ans+=v[a][i%lena]*v[b][i]%mod;\n        // printf(\"Ans=%lld\\n\",Ans);\n        Ans%=mod;\n    }\n    Map[{a,b}]=Ans;\n    // printf(\"Ans=%lld\\n\",Ans);\n    return Ans;\n}\n\nsigned main(){\n    // freopen(\"my.in\",\"r\",stdin);\n    // freopen(\"my.out\",\"w\",stdout);\n    read(n);\n    rep(i,1,n){\n        int len;read(len);rep(j,1,len){int x;read(x);x%=mod;v[i].pb(x);}\n    }\n    Len=sqrt(200000)+1;\n    read(m);\n    rep(i,1,m){\n        int x,y;read(x);read(y);if(v[x].size()&lt;=Len&amp;&amp;v[y].size()&lt;=Len) ans[i]=Solve(x,y);\n        else if(v[x].size()&gt;Len&amp;&amp;v[y].size()&gt;Len) ans[i]=Solve2(x,y);\n        else{\n            if(v[x].size()&lt;v[y].size()) swap(x,y);q[x].pb({y,i});\n        }\n        // if(n==428&amp;&amp;i==33){\n            // printf(\"%d %d\\n\",v[x].size()&lt;=Len,v[y].size()&lt;=Len);exit(0);\n        // }\n    }\n    // exit(0);\n    rep(i,1,n) sort(q[i].begin(),q[i].end());\n    rep(i,1,n){\n        if(q[i].empty()) continue;\n        int l=0;int lenb=v[i].size(),len=q[i].size();\n        while(l&lt;len){\n            int r=l;int nowlen=v[q[i][l].x].size();\n            while(r+1&lt;len&amp;&amp;v[q[i][r+1].x].size()==nowlen) r++;\n            int lena=v[q[i][l].x].size();\n            rep(j,0,lena-1) Tm[j]=0;\n            rep(j,0,lena-1){\n                for(int k=j;k&lt;lenb;k+=lena) Tm[j]=(Tm[j]+v[i][k])%mod;\n            }\n            rep(j,l,r){\n                rep(k,0,lena-1){\n                    ans[q[i][j].id]=(ans[q[i][j].id]+v[q[i][j].x][k]*Tm[k]%mod)%mod;\n                }\n            }\n            l=r+1;\n        }\n    }\n    rep(i,1,m) printf(\"%lld\\n\",ans[i]);\n    return 0;\n}<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n","count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.6k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#t1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">T1</span></a></li></ol>"}